In this article, President Xi Jinping of China and President Donald Trump of the United States make remarks during a meeting at the G20 summit in Hamburg, Germany. President Trump expresses his appreciation for President Xi's efforts in addressing the North Korea issue and emphasizes the importance of trade between the two countries. He believes that they will come to a successful conclusion on trade and eventually achieve success in dealing with North Korea. President Trump also thanks President Xi for the invitation and expresses his honor in getting to know him and his wife.